+- Authorization checks for publish/admin actions use current assignment state.
+
+**Persistence intent**
+Tenant-keyed authorization tables with uniqueness on `(tenant_id, user_id, role_id)`.
+
+### Entity: ActivityEvent
+
+**Description**
